```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant Engine as Simulation Engine
    participant LLM as Groq/Gemini/Mock
    participant Records as Records/Logs

    User->>UI: Configure simulation & press Run
    UI->>Engine: configure(...) / start()
    Engine->>Engine: simulate step (agents act)
    alt LLM mode enabled
        Engine->>LLM: generate agent decisions
        LLM-->>Engine: responses
    else LLM disabled
        Engine-->>Engine: use mock/random decisions
    end
    Engine->>Records: append trade & event logs
    Engine-->>UI: state update (prices, metrics)
    UI-->>User: render charts, leaderboard, forum

```

---

Notes:
- Sequence shows the typical flow per simulation tick; LLM calls are optional and rate-limited.
